replies.body:
{{champion:54}} 
Run around the Rift role playing Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson and be basically immortal. One of my fondest memory was tanking a turret without minion and an enemy Mundo firing at me, I kept calm and killed the turret, all the while blasting in all chat "You throw that cleaver again the rock is gonna take it, turn it sideway and stick it straight up your candy ass". And then I just walk away, not even bothering to fight the Mundo
Oh good time

{{champion:19}} 

It's a concept I was familiar with, and he had a simple kit. but now i've graduated to a completely different character with a much higher skill cap

{{champion:77}}  XD Now i feel like I've gone nowhere. Except I'm climbing that ladder as if gravity was turned upside down...
